						<p>As you start to explain what miracles the Hairmaster 3000&trade; can do, Dr. Williams, who hasn’t yet fallen asleep, interrupts. “Um, from these schematics it seems like you’ve basically just taken the jet engine technology we develop here, and miniaturized it into a hair-dryer???”<br>
						While technically true, you shake off the criticism. “It’s called the HairMASTER, sir. And trust me, it can do much more than that!” This challenge seems to get everyone’s attention. Half of them seem to even want to see it in action. Everyone is looking at you like you’re crazy and you have to win them over somehow…

						</p>
					<div class="choices">Choices:</div>
